content.rendered:
Directed by Nitin Kumar Gupta. Abhay Singhal

Written by Twinkle Agarwal. Anamta-Amaan. Yash eshwari Francis. Nitin Kumar Gupta. Nitin Kumar Gupta. Sohail Haider. Vishal Om Prakash. Alaukik Rahi

Cast Tanmay Ssingh (Rajdeep Randhawa). Musskan Sethi (Mahi). Yograj Singh (Rajdeep’s Father). Upasana Singh (Rajdeep’s Mother (as Upasna Singh)). Virender Commando (Coach Saab). Rahul Roy (Inspector Arsan). Tanmmay Sachdeva (Rajdeep randhawa (as Tanmay ssingh))

Languages Hindi. Russian

Producers Nitin Kumar Gupta. Vikram Jadhav. Kalrashikha. Ashwani Kumar. Shrishti Kumar. Lucky Morani. Mukesh Sachdeva

Production D&T Productio. D&T Production. Lucky Nadiadwala Morani Production
